object.script:
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function pgt(k) return property.getText(k) end
function pgn(k) return property.getNumber(k) end
title=pgt("Title") fmt=pgt("Format string") elwidth=pgn("Element width") elheight=pgn("Element height") gridw=pgn("Grid width") gridh=pgn("Grid height") warnmin=pgn("Warn min") warnmax=pgn("Warn max") ct=gridw*gridh
buf={}
colw=5 rowh=6
posy=0 layoutw=colw*((elwidth+1)*gridw-1)
if #title then posy=posy+rowh*2 end
function onTick() local i for i=1,ct do buf[i]=gn(i) end end
safecol={0,255,0} dangcol={255,0,0}
function scale_color(x,c) return { c[1]*x, c[2]*x,c[3]*x } end
-- updates c to avoid an allocation function add_colors(c,d) c[1]=d[1]+c[1] c[2]=d[2]+c[2] c[3]=d[3]+c[3] return c end
function clamp(v,mn,mx) return math.max(math.min(v,mx),mn) end
function draw_cell(n) local gridx,gridy,gradfac,val,color,color2
val=buf[n] gridx=((n-1)%gridw)+1 gridy=math.floor((n-1)/gridw)+1 gradfac=clamp((val-warnmin)/(warnmax-warnmin),0,1) color=scale_color(1-gradfac,safecol) color2=scale_color(gradfac,dangcol) add_colors(color,color2) screen.setColor(color[1], color[2], color[3])
local x=(elwidth+1)*colw*(gridx-1) local y=(gridy-1)*rowh*elheight screen.drawText(x,posy+y,string.format(fmt, val)) end
function onDraw() local n=1 w=screen.getWidth() if #title then screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawText((layoutw-#title*colw)/2,0,title) end
for n=1,ct do draw_cell(n) end end

object.script:
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function gb(n) return input.getBool(n) end
function sb(n,v) output.setBool(n,v) end
function sn(n,v) output.setNumber(n,v) end
devct=5 function devinit() local tmp={} local i
for i=1,devct do tmp[i]={level=0,cap=0,rate=0,leak=false} end return tmp end
devs=devinit() function onTick() local i,j,obj,klax
klax=false j=1 for i=1,devct do obj=devs[i] obj.level=gn(j) j=j+1 obj.cap=gn(j) j=j+1 obj.rate=gn(j) j=j+1 obj.leak=gb(i) klax=klax or obj.leak end
balset=gn(32) for i=1,devct do sn(i,devs[i].cap*balset/100) end sb(32,klax) end
function drawsub(x,y,l,h) screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawCircle(x+l-h/2,y+h/2,h/2) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(x,y, l-h/2,h) screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawRect(x,y,l-h/2,h) screen.drawLine(x+l-h/2,y,x+l-h/2,y+h) end
colw=5 rowh=6 function compartment(x,y,obj) screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawText(x,y,string.format("%3.0f/%3.0f%%\n" .. "%+6.0fL/s",obj.level*100/obj.cap,balset,obj.rate)) if not obj.leak then screen.setColor(16,16,16) end screen.drawText(x,y+rowh*2, " LEAK") end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight()
sh=h*.5 sw=w-1 y=rowh*3 x=0 drawsub(x,y,sw,sh) compartment(x+sw*.4,y-rowh*3,devs[1]) compartment(x+sw*.4,y+rowh*8+2,devs[2]) compartment(x+sw*.4+colw*10,y-rowh*3,devs[3]) compartment(x+sw*.1,y-rowh*3,devs[4]) compartment(x+sw*.1,y+rowh*8+2,devs[5]) end

function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function sn(n,x) output.setNumber(n,x) end
function onTick() vlevel=gn(1) vcap=gn(2) bat=gn(3)*100 radiation=gn(4) vestemp=gn(5) ttemp=gn(6) rodext=gn(7) batdelta=gn(8) * 100 * 60 sn(6, math.log(ttemp) / math.log(42908)) end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight()
local str=string.format("REACTOR STATUS

" ..
"Level %5.2f%%
" .. " %5.0f L/%5.0f L

" .. "PWR %7.2f
" .. "TEMP %7.2f
" .. "TARG %7.2f
" .. "RAD %7.2f
" .. "BAT %7.2f %+5.2f", vlevel/vcap*100,vlevel,vcap,(1-rodext)*100,vestemp,ttemp,radiation,bat,batdelta) screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,0,w,h,str) end

object.script:
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function gb(n) return input.getBool(n) end
function onTick() pressure=gn(1) boiltemp=gn(2) boilvol=gn(3) rpm=gn(4)*60 bat=gn(5)*100 condtemp=gn(6) condvol=gn(7) condpump=gn(8)*100 gen=gn(9) inlet=gb(1) end
colw=5 rowh=6
function onoff_color(b) if b then screen.setColor(0,255,0) else screen.setColor(24,24,24) end end
function onDraw()
local title="POWER STATUS" w=screen.getWidth() screen.setColor(0,255,0)
screen.drawText((w-#title*colw)/2,0,title)
local str=string.format(" BOILER CONDENSE\n" .. "PRES %5.2f ---\n" .. "TEMP %5.1f %5.1f\n" .. " VOL %5.2f %5.2f\n\n" ..
"RPM %4.0f BAT %6.2f\n" .. "GEN %4.1f COOL %3.0f%%", pressure,boiltemp,condtemp,boilvol,condvol,rpm,bat,gen,condpump) screen.drawText(0,rowh*2,str) onoff_color(inlet) screen.drawText(0,rowh*10-2,"INLET") end
